OL,5, The chairman of the BBC says he won't  
OL,6, quit over the Boris Johnson loan row.  
OL,8,FRichard Sharp is accused of helping    
OL,9,Ffacilitate a loan to the then prime    
OL,10,Fminister, when Mr Sharp was applying to
OL,11,Fbe BBC chairman.                       
OL,13,FHis appointment is now under review by 
OL,14,Fthe Commissioner of Public             
OL,15,FAppointments.                          
OL,17,FMr Sharp denies being involvedin any   
OL,18,Floan and told the BBC he believes he   
OL,19,Fwill be exonerated because he "was     
OL,20,Fappointed on merit".                   
